description:
Your inner fashion designer will rejoice with the newest DLC for "Fashion World", an exclusive set of 20 all-new levels of puzzles, there to mix and match like never before.

Set your gala looks in motion and capture them in photo mode with your eyes up to the stars. Get lit up as the most fabulous fashionista in the world of glittering glamour with the "Glamour Gala" Expansion
name: Fashion World DLC 1: Glamour Gala
